io.netty.handler.codec.http.websocketx

Interface WebSocketFrameEncoder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChannelHandler, ChannelOutboundHandler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WebSocket00FrameEncoder, WebSocket07FrameEncoder, WebSocket08FrameEncoder, WebSocket13FrameEncoder

    public interface WebSocketFrameEncoder
extends ChannelOutboundHandler
    Marker interface which all WebSocketFrame encoders need to implement. This makes it easier to access the added encoder later in the ChannelPipeline.
